05:12.708 --> 05:16.542
Rick Lagina's brother Marty,
along with Matty Blake,

05:16.708 --> 05:19.500
have explored
the Poverty Island area

05:19.625 --> 05:22.000
with local treasure hunter
Bob Kreipke as he attempted

05:22.167 --> 05:23.500
to locate
the underwater wreckage

05:23.583 --> 05:25.167
of the <i>Captain Lawrence.</i>

05:25.250 --> 05:28.042
Well, he can't
bring it up though, can he?

05:28.208 --> 05:29.500
NARRATOR:
But despite uncovering

05:29.583 --> 05:31.583
some very promising clues,

05:31.708 --> 05:34.083
finding the remains of
the lost ship,

05:34.208 --> 05:36.042
