14:23.125 --> 14:25.000
We use our side-scan sonar.

14:25.083 --> 14:27.167
See what's actually down there

14:27.333 --> 14:29.458
beneath that wreck
where it's deeper,

14:29.583 --> 14:31.375
where we can't see from the air.

14:31.500 --> 14:33.333
And then, hopefully,
identify some targets to dive.

14:33.417 --> 14:36.375
MATTY:
Right now, I want to land,
you know, because

14:36.500 --> 14:38.500
I've seen it from above,
