14:48.042 --> 14:49.333
that could do a side scan?

14:49.417 --> 14:51.167
-A friend of ours, Todd Berg.
-Okay.

14:51.250 --> 14:52.667
He'll get us a side scan
all set up and ready

14:52.833 --> 14:54.167
to go on the boat.

14:54.292 --> 14:56.667
If we can definitively say,

14:56.750 --> 14:57.958
"That's the <i>Lawrence,"</i>

14:58.083 --> 14:59.375
that would be huge.

14:59.500 --> 15:01.333
-MATTY: That is huge.
