the team will
be traveling 13 miles

15:41.542 --> 15:44.000
back out to the coast
off Poverty Island,

15:44.125 --> 15:47.292
where they will hopefully
pinpoint a more exact location

15:47.375 --> 15:49.042
of the wreck they
viewed from the skies

15:49.208 --> 15:50.333
earlier this morning,

15:50.500 --> 15:51.875
and gather more data

15:52.042 --> 15:55.292
in preparation for
a potential dive operation.

