You know what I mean?
You're telling the story.

20:02.000 --> 20:04.208
And it's emerging right before
our eyes, it's incredible.

20:04.333 --> 20:07.000
All right, so,
I mean, we've seen it

20:07.083 --> 20:08.667
from it from the air.
(chuckles)

20:08.833 --> 20:11.208
We've seen it with our eyes,
