20:36.708 --> 20:38.500
and get back out here tomorrow
morning and just get at it.

20:38.625 --> 20:41.417
-All right.
-Great day!

20:42.333 --> 20:43.917
RICK:
It's been a great day.

20:48.167 --> 20:49.292
NARRATOR:
The next morning...

20:49.417 --> 20:50.583
MATTY:
Let's get in that water.

20:50.708 --> 20:52.667
NARRATOR:
...Mike and Jess Groleau,

20:52.792 --> 20:55.708
along with Rick Lagina
and Matty Blake,

20:55.875 --> 20:58.500
return to the waters just off
the coast of Poverty Island

20:58.583 --> 21:01.333
to begin their
underwater dive operation.

