NARRATOR:
He will be helping the team

21:18.583 --> 21:20.458
to hopefully find
and confirm the existence

21:20.542 --> 21:24.000
of two shipwrecks
identified during yesterday's

21:24.167 --> 21:25.833
side-scan sonar search.

21:25.917 --> 21:27.000
JON:
Okay, you ready?

21:27.125 --> 21:28.167
GROLEAU:
So the first dive

21:28.250 --> 21:30.833
