NARRATOR:
Just off the shores

25:48.583 --> 25:49.792
of Poverty Island,

25:49.875 --> 25:52.625
treasure hunter Mike Groleau

25:52.750 --> 25:55.833
has just alerted Rick Lagina
and Matty Blake

25:55.917 --> 25:58.167
that he has come across
a second unidentified shipwreck

25:58.333 --> 26:00.208
at the bottom of
Lake Michigan.

26:00.375 --> 26:01.333
MATTY:
That's great news, fellas.

26:01.500 --> 26:02.583
Two ships is good.

26:02.708 --> 26:03.833
Great work, keep going.

26:03.958 --> 26:05.583
NARRATOR:
The team is hoping

26:05.708 --> 26:07.958
that this could be
the <i>Captain Lawrence,</i>

26:08.042 --> 26:12.042
