26:12.167 --> 26:14.583
after it was believed
to have recovered

26:14.708 --> 26:18.458
nearly $400 million
in lost Civil War gold

26:18.542 --> 26:21.000
from another shipwreck,
before it too sank

26:21.125 --> 26:23.958
